// All trading times are in UTC+3 timezone
// Market sessions in UTC+3:
//   Early London: 11:00-15:30 UTC+3
//   Gap period: 15:30-17:30 UTC+3 (lower quality, skipped in DUAL_WINDOW mode)
//   London-NY Overlap: 17:30-19:30 UTC+3 (highest volatility)

//---------------- DAY FILTER (V7) ----------------//
// Consistent schedule: Same trading hours Mon-Fri
// Saturday/Sunday: No trading (market closed/closing)

