// V7: Simplified - No special Monday/Saturday windows
// Monday-Friday: Standard dual window (11:00-15:30 + 17:30-19:30)
// Saturday: No trading (market closes at 01:00 UTC+3, before our windows)
// Sunday: No trading (market closed)

//---------------- SAFETY --------------//

